graph TB
    Start([Business Problem]) --> Define[1. Problem Definition]
    Define --> Collect[2. Data Collection]
    Collect --> Explore[3. Data Exploration]
    Explore --> Prepare[4. Data Preparation]
    Prepare --> Model[5. Modeling]
    Model --> Evaluate[6. Evaluation]
    
    Evaluate --> Decision{Good Enough?}
    Decision -->|No| Iterate[Iterate]
    Iterate --> Prepare
    Decision -->|Yes| Deploy[7. Deployment]
    
    Deploy --> Monitor[8. Monitoring]
    Monitor --> Check{Performance OK?}
    Check -->|Yes| Monitor
    Check -->|No| Retrain[Retrain Model]
    Retrain --> Collect
    
    Deploy --> End([Production System])
    
    style Define fill:#e1f5ff
    style Model fill:#ffe1e1
    style Deploy fill:#e1ffe1
    style Monitor fill:#fff4e1